com.mewna.catnip.cache.view

Class CompositeCacheView<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mewna.catnip.cache.view.CompositeCacheView<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the entity held by this cache.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CacheView<T>, Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompositeNamedCacheView

    public class CompositeCacheView<T>
extends Object
implements CacheView<T>
    A CacheView that's equivalent to a collection of provided ones. Any update to any of the provided views will update this view.
    Since:
    12/15/18
    Author:
    natanbc
